'''涼宮春日'''（{{jpn|j=涼宮 ハルヒ|hg=すずみや はるひ|rm=Suzumiya Haruhi}}）是《[[涼宮春日系列|涼宮春日系列]]》[[輕小說|輕小說]]及相關動畫《[[涼宮春日的憂鬱|涼宮春日的憂鬱]]》的主角，為[[西宮市|西宮市]]{{tsl|ja|兵庫県立西宮北高等学校|兵庫縣立西宮北高等學校|北高}}二年五班的學生，擁有改變世界的能力，但本人並不知道這點。<ref>{{cite web|first=Felicity|last=Hughes|url=http://blog.japantimes.co.jp/japan-pulse/akihabara-maids-get-slap-happy/|title=Where maids get slap happy...for a price|publisher=Japan Pulse|date=September 30, 2009|accessdate=February 2, 2010|archive-date=2011-07-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110716104159/http://blog.japantimes.co.jp/japan-pulse/akihabara-maids-get-slap-happy/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.popcultureshock.com/manga/index.php/reviews/sigh-haruhi-suzumiya/|title=The Sigh of Haruhi Suzumiya and the Haruhi Manga|publisher=Popculture Shock|date=June 15, 2009|accessdate=February 2, 2010|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120308093206/http://www.popcultureshock.com/manga/index.php/reviews/sigh-haruhi-suzumiya/|archivedate=2012年3月8日}}</ref><ref name="Anime Top">{{cite web |url=http://uk.movies.ign.com/articles/103/1036651p2.html |title=Top 25 Anime Characters of All Time |author=Chris Mackenzie |date=October 20, 2009 |work=[[IGN|IGN]] |accessdate=April 9, 2011 |archive-date=2009-10-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091024220803/http://uk.movies.ign.com/articles/103/1036651p2.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/interest/2011-01-12/eva-haruhi-heroes-donate-to-tiger-mask-movement|title=''Eva'', ''Haruhi'' Heroes Donate to ''Tiger Mask'' Movement|publisher=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]]|date=January 12, 2011|accessdate=January 20, 2011|archive-date=2021-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210411125738/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/interest/2011-01-12/eva-haruhi-heroes-donate-to-tiger-mask-movement|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==介紹==
